oneOf.description:
An execution-grounded verdict was reached for a run's diff. The load-bearing
`verdict` and `checks` reuse the canonical [`crate::verdict`] types;
`advisory_llm_judge`, when present, is non-load-bearing (INV-R1).

attestation.description:
How completely the run was attested: `Full` = captured by Nerve's recorder;
`Partial` = reconstructed from an external OTel trace (L5 ingest). Skipped
when `Full`, so existing serialized runs round-trip byte-identically.
